# DESCRIPTION
# Find all possible values for which the matrix is diagonalizable.
# ENDDESCRIPTION

## DBsubject(Linear algebra)
## DBchapter(Matrix factorizations)
## DBsection(Diagonalization)
## Institution(University of Missouri-Columbia)
## Author(Rick Lynch)
## Level(3)
